# Wordpress snippets

This project contains all kind of small scripts that work within the snippets plugin for wordpress

## Getting Started

These scripts work out of the box. Just install the snippets plugin.
Copy and paste the code from one of the files.
Save and activate (frontend or backend)

### Prerequisites

You only need the snippets plugin from
https://nl.wordpress.org/plugins/code-snippets/

### Installing

Copy the code within the file. Create a new snippet in wordpress. Paste the code in the new snippet. Save and activate.

